#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Invoice Clients</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ອອກໃບເກັບເງິນໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າ</strong>"

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Invoice the client</strong>: Compile logged hours, document "
"preparation costs, and travel expenses into the invoice."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ອອກໃບເກັບເງິນໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າ</strong>: ລວບລວມຊົ່ວໂມງທີ່ບັນທຶກໄວ້, ຄ່າກະກຽມເອກະສານ, ແລະ ຄ່"
"າເດີນທາງ ເຂົ້າໃນໃບເກັບເງິນ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Log your time</strong> directly in the 'Timesheet' tab of a specific"
" task, or use the timer to track the time spent on that task."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ບັນທຶກເວລາຂອງເຈົ້າ</strong> ໂດຍກົງໃນແທັບ 'ໃບບັນທຶກເວລາ' (Timesheet) ຂອງວຽກໃດໜຶ່"
"ງ, ຫຼື ໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງມືຈັບເວລາເພື່ອຕິດຕາມເວລາທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນວຽກນັ້ນ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Log your time</strong>: Track hours spent on each task in the "
"Timesheet tab."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ບັນທຶກເວລາຂອງເຈົ້າ</strong>: ຕິດຕາມຊົ່ວໂມງທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນແຕ່ລະວຽກໃນແທັບໃບບັນທຶກເວລາ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Manage documents</strong>: Upload and organize case documents in the"
" project’s document folder."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຈັດການເອກະສານ</strong>: ອັບໂຫລດ ແລະ ຈັດລະບຽບເອກະສານຄະດີໃນໂຟນເດີເອກະສານຂອງໂ"
"ຄງການ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Manage tasks</strong> by organizing them into stages such as 'To "
