#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.aboutus
msgid "Tony Fred"
msgstr "Tony Fred"

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model:product.template,name:industry_lawyer.product_product_7_product_template
msgid "Travel Expenses"
msgstr "ຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍໃນການເດີນທາງ"

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:sale.order.template,note:industry_lawyer.sale_order_template_1
msgid "Travel expenses: 80€/hour"
msgstr "ຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍໃນການເດີນທາງ: 80€/ຊົ່ວໂມງ"

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>CRM app</strong> to manage client interactions and conduct "
"the required <strong>Know Your Customer (KYC) assessment</strong> before "
"accepting a case."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບ CRM</strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການການພົວພັນກັບລູກຄ້າ ແລະ ດຳເນີນ <strong>ການປະເມີນ "
"KYC</strong> ທີ່ຈຳເປັນ ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຮັບຄະດີ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>Expenses App</strong> to keep track of all firm-related "
"costs in one place, such as a restaurant with a client or office supplies. "
"This ensures internal expenses remain transparent and easy to manage."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍ</strong> ເພື່ອຕິດຕາມທຸກຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບບໍລິສັດໄວ້ໃນບ່ອນດຽວ ເຊັ່ນ ກ"
"ານໄປຮ້ານອາຫານກັບລູກຄ້າ ຫຼື ອຸປະກອນຫ້ອງການ. ນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍພາຍໃນມີຄວາມໂປ່ງໃສ ແລະ ຈັດການໄດ້"
"ງ່າຍ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>Sign App</strong> to request a signature from the partner to"
" approve the completed legal documents before delivery and invoicing the "
"client."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບເຊັນເອກະສານ</strong> ເພື່ອຮ້ອງຂໍການເຊັນຊື່ຈາກຮຸ້ນສ່ວນ ເພື່ອອະນຸມັດເອກະສານທາງກົດ"
"ໝາຍທີ່ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ ກ່ອນຈະສົ່ງມອບ ແລະ ອອກໃບເກັບເງິນໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>Website App</strong> to enhance your law firm’s online "
"visibility and make it easy for clients to contact you."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບເວັບໄຊ</strong> ເພື່ອເພີ່ມການເຫັນບໍລິສັດກົດໝາຍຂອງເຈົ້າທາງອອນລາຍ ແລະ ເຮັດໃຫ້ລູກ"
"ຄ້າຕິດຕໍ່ເຈົ້າໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>timer functionality</strong> to track time spent on a "
"specific client case."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong>ຟັງຊັນຈັບເວລາ</strong> ເພື່ອຕິດຕາມເວລາທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນຄະດີໃດໜຶ່ງຂອງລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the<strong> <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Sign App</font></strong> to "
"securely sign engagement letters and legal documents, ensuring clear "
"agreements before or after legal work."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong> <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບເຊັນເອກະສານ</font></strong> ເພື່ອເ"
"ຊັນໜັງສືມອບໝາຍວຽກ ແລະ ເອກະສານທາງກົດໝາຍຢ່າງປອດໄພ, ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນຂໍ້ຕົກລົງທີ່ຊັດເຈນກ່ອນ ຫຼື ຫຼັງການເຮັ"
"ດວຽກທາງກົດໝາຍ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Using down payment for provision:"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ເງິນຈ່າຍລ່ວງໜ້າສຳລັບຄ່າບໍລິການ:"

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.homepage
msgid ""
"We focus on thorough research and strategic planning, ensuring comprehensive"
" legal representation that meets industry standards."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາເນັ້ນການຄົ້ນຄວ້າຢ່າງລະອຽດ ແລະ ການວາງແຜນຍຸດທະສາດ, ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນການເປັນຕົວແທນທາງກົດໝາຍທີ່"
"ຄົບຖ້ວນ ແລະ ໄດ້ມາດຕະຖານສາກົນ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.homepage
msgid ""
"We provide expert legal representation, ensuring your rights are protected "
"in every case we handle."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາໃຫ້ບໍລິການເປັນຕົວແທນທາງກົດໝາຍໂດຍຜູ້ຊ່ຽວຊານ, ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າສິດທິຂອງເຈົ້າຈະຖືກປົກປ້ອງໃນທຸກຄະດີ"
"ທີ່ພວກເຮົາມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມ."

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:industry_lawyer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome to the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Odoo Law Firm "
"package</font></strong>!"
msgstr ""
"ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບເຂົ້າສູ່ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແພັກເກດ Odoo ສຳລັບບໍລິສັດກົດໝາ"
"ຍ</font></strong>!"

#. module: industry_lawyer
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:industry_lawyer.knowledge_tour
